<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_86e01407-bd2f-47d2-8ffa-41556bf0ee4f" outputclass="ncc-clause"><sptc>C1P7</sptc><title id="_90447ab9-b1c8-4648-af0f-263297f800c1">Damage</title><archive-num>2019: CP1.1</archive-num><subclause id="_98603073-99a0-43af-a76c-a5410a441ce4" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_ba964653-70b4-4d2d-8372-09df172b6ce4">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Damage to a sanitary <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1401_0.7.0.xml#_a318c0f3-5635-4ac0-b103-59d798c9f23d" id="_1a3c71d3-16ac-4c2d-9e18-8feea3b00c2e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">plumbing</xref> system from superimposed loads, ground movement or root penetration must be avoided.</p></subclause><callout id="_2f9945cd-9f19-45f5-b219-ffdec4814b07"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><p>Superimposed loads that a sanitary <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1401_0.7.0.xml#_a318c0f3-5635-4ac0-b103-59d798c9f23d" id="_e8eac0de-f250-4483-b1de-414990980603" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">plumbing</xref> system is susceptible to damage from, include building loads and loads arising from building movement or ground movement.</p></callout></clause>